&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;If you&#39;re energised by opening doors, sparking real conversations with hospitality decision-makers, and building pipeline that drives meaningful business — this is your role. As a BDR on Duetto&#39;s EMEA team, you&#39;ll be the first point of contact for potential customers across the region: qualifying inbound leads, running targeted outbound campaigns, and partnering closely with Regional Sales Managers to turn prospects into qualified opportunities. It&#39;s a high-activity, high-impact role with real visibility into how a global SaaS sales engine works.&lt;/p&gt;
