&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll generate and qualify new business opportunities across EMEA through proactive outbound outreach — email, phone, social, and events — researching target accounts, identifying buyer personas, and tailoring messaging to uncover real pain points and convert prospects into qualified pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
