&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll maintain accurate activity and pipeline data in Salesforce, tracking calls, emails, connections, and meetings to ensure visibility, forecast accuracy, and continuous performance optimisation.&lt;/li&gt;
