&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Senior Marketing Manager, EMEA&lt;/strong&gt; is responsible for owning and executing Duetto’s regional marketing strategy across EMEA — driving integrated, high-impact programs that align with revenue goals and accelerate pipeline. This role sits at the intersection of field marketing, demand generation, and sales alignment, requiring both strategic thinking and hands-on execution. The ideal candidate is a collaborative builder who thrives in a high-growth environment, brings genuine passion for the hospitality industry, and is energized by the opportunity to create a scalable regional marketing engine from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
